							<p>
								These two UN sdg goals are similar. They both are about trying to improve the earth and what lives on it. The Life Under Water Sdg is on the affect humans are having on humans and how we are destroying the precious oceans. The Climate Action Sdg is about the affect humans are having on the Earth and mainly global warming. They also look at what could be the extinction of many different species. As some species of fish would die with how we treat ocean and some sensitive animals would not make it out alive of this heat wave. 
							</p>
